        "rich_text_aFNT3c": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>A New Era in Diamond Jewelry Buying </h2><p>Until today, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/jewelry\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Jewelry\">jewelry</a> had always been associated to traditions, weddings and family legacies. Today, we are in an era where buying <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Jewelry\">Lab Grown Diamond Jewelry</a> in India doesn’t have to be related to an upcoming occasion. Women are rewriting rules inside homes and in boardrooms, and while they do that, jewelry is the reward they have always looked forward to. At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, we don’t see this as a trend, but a spark of a movement. A movement that celebrates women and the shine she brings to life!</p>",
            "custom_id": "newera"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dytMpG": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Women Are Choosing To Self Gift Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Women Are Choosing To Self Gift Jewelry</h2>",
            "custom_id": "selfgift"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zxLBXi": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Self_Gift.jpg",
            "text": "<p>For decades, jewelry was associated with marriage or a gift to be received by women. Jewelry is now an extension of self identity - completing the look, bringing poise and grace in every movement, and a statement in itself. Gifting jewelry to oneself is a mark of achievement, a decision to know her worth, and the quiet elegance that jewelry brings to every outfit. Self gifting Lab Grown Diamond jewelry is not just indulgence, or retail therapy. It can symbolize a career milestone, a smart investment in timeless luxury and a chance to express one’s style and taste. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_HGC6EB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When you choose jewelry for yourself, it is a quiet reminder that you chose this for you. The diamond bracelet or the women diamond earrings that you buy for yourself, is not just about beauty but also about autonomy, a mark of self love. Every milestone big or small deserves recognition. Women are not waiting for external validation, but investing in jewelry that will remain as keepsakes for different milestones - finishing a degree, starting a business, or even simply rewarding yourself for personal growth. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        }
